text: Henk Nooren (born 23 August 1954) is a Dutch equestrian. He competed in two events at the 1976 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1954 births Category:Living people Category:Dutch male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of the Netherlands Category:Equestrians at the 1976 Summer Olympics Category:People from Bergen, Limburg
